* Added refresh after toggling Alternete Speeds Limits

* Added all translations for Alternative Speeds Limits
* Changed license to GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0, in order to be compatible with Google libraries.

* Fixed issues related to search in tablets

* Commented log messages
